{"tid":2167223,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 迷你油炸鬼","createTime":"2020-08-21T03:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T12:26:15.000Z","uid":30742,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2355c4de1f1a7a4f874d0cb3e802407e6b24780f","tid":2167223,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iST1d3o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiST1d3o.jpg&h=d39780ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ufp4Z11OmcA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUfp4Z11OmcA&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=5853c646\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ufp4Z11OmcA</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係facebook朋友想我整既！ <br />\n佢要做比老公食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果我足足整左三次，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到某人點頭話可以喇 <br />\n做到外脆內軟喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我先有得剪呢條片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有排都唔會再食油炸鬼 <br />\n其實講真就真係唔算難， 係個麵團個質感要留意，<br />\n其他都無咩難度 材料都幾簡單，而家油器咁貴 偶然係屋企玩下都過癮既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文字食譜：<a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2020/08/mini-fried-dough-stick-english.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F08%2Fmini-fried-dough-stick-english.html&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=05badcd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2020/08/mini-fried-dough-stick-english.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=cc88fb57\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a> Instagram:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=4f4f0120\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a>  Blog:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=b9f0b416\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"868477f2420ac45d3715e84317a8c05cd18896a7","tid":2167223,"uid":34489,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"頭香..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97080e31153fc1edf605f0fc02f3b174a2d7174a","tid":2167223,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:26:16.000Z","msg":"IG隻倉鼠頭像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca21478c12676ff8b984a1183a7413eb9979e6d","tid":2167223,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97080e31153fc1edf605f0fc02f3b174a2d7174a","tid":2167223,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:26:16.000Z","msg":"IG隻倉鼠頭像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:30:01.000Z","msg":"阿八走左好耐了&hellip;&hellip;我都仲好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},